Developer Terms of Use
des:
Get the latest information from Live 5 News Charleston, South Carolina within Alexa's Flash Briefing.

Enable this Skill, then say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing" or "Alexa, what's in the news" to hear the audio.

Feeds include the latest weather forecast for the Charleston, South Carolina area from the WCSC Live 5 Weather team.
